MyBroadband has partnered with Seagate to promote their FireCuda gaming products, and is giving away several FireCuda products to lucky MyBroadband readers. To enter, simply follow these steps: The following prizes are up for grabs: 4TB storage hub that connects your entire battlestation via one Thunderbolt 3 cable  2TB gaming hard drive with customisable RGB LED lighting. 5TB gaming hard drive with customisable RGB LED lighting.  The competition will end on 29 June 2021, and standard MyBroadband Forum competition rules apply.